headline.main: ENVOY OFF TO PARIS; Darlan Is Expected to Get Demand for Laval's Return EARLY DECISION IS SEEN Extent of the 'Collaboration' by Petain Likely to Be Fixed by Hitler

abstract: Adm Darlan leaves for Paris; Laval return expected to be chief demand; Paris antagonism to Vichy discussed
